What a find! solar paid in full and a refreshing pool!
Older established neighborhood, this 3br/2bth has a formal LR with masonry FP, roomy den and enclosed patio with extra receptacles for all the electronics the family needs.  It also features  handicap access to front entry and main suite bathroom is equipped with handicap cabinets, shower, and closet.  This home conveniently placed near Best Buy Grocery and schools on Tulare Ave. and Conyer.  Call today for your appointment.
